Package: cpmr
Title: Tidymodels Engines for Connectome Predictive Modeling
Version: 0.1.1.9000
Authors@R:
    person("Liang", "Zhang", , "psychelzh@outlook.com", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0001-9041-1150"))
Description: Provides a tidymodels interface for connectome-based
    predictive modeling (CPM) (Shen et al. (2017)
    <doi:10.1038/nprot.2016.178>). The package registers a parsnip model
    specification, integrates with workflows and tune, exposes CPM-aware
    performance metrics, and keeps the core edge-selection and
    train/predict steps leakage-safe within resampling.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
URL: https://github.com/psychelzh/cpmr, https://psychelzh.github.io/cpmr/
